# Per-rung scratch dirs (`rootless`: staged store + DB snapshot; `oci-load`:
# OCI layouts + corrupted-archive control; `td-builder`: staged store +
# registration record; `generation-image`: validator image extraction; `run`:
# archive + unpacked rootfs); kept on a red run for triage, removed on green.
.rootless-scratch/
.oci-load-scratch/
.td-builder-scratch/
.genimg-scratch/
.run-scratch/
